  <Summary>The Dead of the Night: Doug Carter hops a train to run away from home when he finds that the train he hopped is a ghostly version of President Lincoln's funeral train.

The Phantom in Our Family: Did the ghost of Joey Rodriguez, killed in Vietnam, return to his mother?

The Fangs of the Phantoms: District Officer Fontaine must transport two native killers to justice, but do they have the power to turn into jungle animals?

One Foot Over the Grave: A witch places a curse on Colonel Buck.

